{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_01","textHome":"我是在名叫杜鹃之家的孤儿院被养大的，@在那之前的事情我都已经不记得了。因为都是@1岁时候的事情了，况且我还是被人抛弃。@好像是在拉面店后面丢弃的鸡骨旁被发现的。@很过分对吧……不过，我倒是很喜欢拉面的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_18","textHome":"我最近，在做一个很大的雕刻。啊……不过@已经不能算是刻了吧，感觉差不多是削。@因为我在用电锯做！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_19","textHome":"这样子我一定是变强了对吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_20","textHome":"我懂了我懂了！有些……不一样的感觉呢！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_21","textHome":"我从以前开始就是这样，心里想的要么立马@说出来，要么就会体现在表情上，一直都@改不过来……不过，这也算是我的特点吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_22","textHome":"对我来说，养育我的老师就如同真正的母亲@一样。温柔，总是挂着笑容，我最喜欢她了。@但是，她已经不在人世了……所以，@我要连同老师的份一起活下去才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_23","textHome":"在我一个人无精打采的时候，木叶和叶月……@还有杜鹃花之家的大家总是在鼓励我……@对我来说，他们就如同家人一样。所以，@我要为了我的家人打起精神！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_24","textHome":"早啊！状态怎么样？我已经干劲十足了！@就等你来了哦！那么走吧！……去哪里？@啊……总之走就行了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_25","textHome":"早上早上早上好——！试着连打三次招呼！…@早上第一件事就是……吃我一拳！@怎么样？醒了吗？要再来一拳吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_26","textHome":"午饭——！我饿啦——！肚子已经咕噜咕噜的@叫了！我已经准备好大吃一顿了！@不管吃什么都行啦——！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_27","textHome":"晚饭——！……在此之前先退治魔女。不过，@也没办法……这个时候就该说@「谁让这是工作呢」对吧。@我之前在电视剧里见过。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_03","textHome":"这不是很有趣嘛！我的斗志燃烧起来了——！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_28","textHome":"呜哦——！好困！晚上好困！我虽然早上@很有精神，但到了晚上就不行了。好啦，@我差不多该睡了。我睡啦？3、2、1……呼"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_29","textHome":"我和叶月还有木叶，每天都在拼命活着。@我们三人，已经下定决心了。所以，@只要还清醒着我们就会全力以赴！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_30","textHome":"什么什么？是要做些什么了吧！太好了，@这不是有趣嘛！虽然我不是很明白，@总之先去做吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_31","textHome":"想和我战斗吗？没问题，来吧！但是@先说好了。我，可不会手下留情，@我会全力以赴的哦~！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_32","textHome":"要和这里的大家战斗吗！就像节日祭典一样？@好呀好呀，是热闹的节日！太好了！@气氛高涨起来了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_33","textHome":"快看快看！是蝗虫！在准备起飞的时候@被我抓住了！徒手哦！我才不需要捕虫网啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_34","textHome":"你吸过花蜜吗？很甜很美味哦！我最喜欢@的味道是杜鹃花蜜。因为老师以前@总是会给我这个。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_35","textHome":"我虽然不会做饭，但我最喜欢吃了！过去，@我能吃下300份碗子荞麦面！……只不过，@吃完就倒下了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_36","textHome":"世界上有很多擅长战斗的动物对吧。@我正在研究这个。也在参考它们的战斗方式。@熊啊狼啊之类的……甚至还有考拉哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_37","textHome":"神滨市，不仅充满了魔女，也有不少@魔法少女呢。不过毋庸置疑！@我们是最强的队伍！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_04","textHome":"咕——！怎么总是平手！下次一定要@决出胜负！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_38","textHome":"怎么回事啊，那个叫菲莉希亚的人！@只是看到了她的脸，就有种@不想输的心情涌了上来！为什么啊——！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_39","textHome":"决斗果然是最能让人燃烧斗志的！就算是@谁先数到100这种微不足道的比试，@也能让人情绪高涨啊~"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_40","textHome":"过去不管发生什么我都会立刻顶撞回去。@不过现在我已经是大人了啊……诶？没变吗？@才没有那回事！才没有那回事呢!"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_41","textHome":"偶尔！…只是偶尔，我也想要穿一次连衣裙。@嘿嘿，因为我也算是淑女啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":302800,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_42","textHome":"嘿嘿~！我会把它们收拾干净的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_43","textHome":"太好了太好了！我做的怎么样~！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_44","textHome":"呼，干净利落，对吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_45","textHome":"早就说啦！……我是最强的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_46","textHome":"轻松拿下了呢！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_63","textHome":"好的！粗野的招式，要来喽！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_05","textHome":"没办法，只好承认了！神滨也有高手在啊！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":302800,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3028_00_64","textHome":"我就放手去做，把这家伙解决吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":